PN,31101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,FThe man behind the voice technology
OL,7,Ffor Alexa says he was inspired by TV
OL,8,Fshows like Star Trek, where people had
OL,9,Fconversations with computers.
OL,11,FNow, thanks to William Tunstall-
OL,12,FPedoe's invention, conversations with
OL,13,Fcomputers are commonplace.
OL,15,FHowever, in an interview with ITV News
OL,16,FScience Editor Martin Stew, Tunstall-
OL,17,FPedoe warns that soon we may no longer
OL,18,Fbe able to trust our eyes and ears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"When I was building Alexa in 2012, if
OL,7,Fyou wanted to create an automatic
OL,8,Fvoice of a real person, you needed
OL,9,Fthem to sit in a sound studio for two
OL,10,Fweeks and pay #100,000 to make a
OL,11,Fcomputer version of their voice,"
OL,12,FTunstall-Pedoe explained.
OL,14,F"Now all you need is a two-second
OL,15,Fsample of their voice, and you can use
OL,16,Fopen source software to clone their
OL,17,Fvoice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"And it will not be that long before
OL,7,Fyou're on a video call with someone
OL,8,Fand you won't even be sure that you're
OL,9,Ftalking to a real person. You will
OL,10,Fneed to actually be in person, face-to-
OL,11,Fface, to know that you're actually
OL,12,Ftalking to a human."
OL,14,FFor some, that is a very worrying
OL,15,Fprospect, and the solutions are not
OL,16,Fobvious.
OL,18,F"I just think the world needs to adapt
OL,19,Fthat when you see a video, you realise
OL,20,Fit might be fake" he told ITV News.
OL,26,@|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"I don't think people should be
OL,7,Fterrified. I think they should be
OL,8,Fconcerned but it should not rise
OL,9,Fbeyond that. Society will adapt."
OL,11,FTunstall-Pedoe left Amazon in 2016
OL,12,Fand, in 2019, launched a new company
OL,13,Fcalled UnlikelyAI.
OL,15,FThe aim is to make an AI which does
OL,16,Fnot have so-called "hallucinations" -
OL,17,Fwhen it comes up with believable but
OL,18,Fultimately false answers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,FBy combining two types of technology,
OL,7,Fthe company is developing an AI which
OL,8,Fdoes not need to be double-checked,
OL,9,Ffreeing time up for the businesses
OL,10,Fthat use it.
OL,12,FTunstall-Pedoe thinks that could be
OL,13,Fworth significant amounts of money to
OL,14,Fthe economy.
OL,16,F"There's literally trillions of
OL,17,Fdollars of value locked behind what we
OL,18,Fcall the trust ceiling," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"The lack of trust is preventing the
OL,7,Ffull automation of business processes
OL,8,Fand preventing people fully embracing
OL,9,FAI.
OL,11,F"We estimate that just in the UK,
OL,12,Fthere's #29 billion worth of value per
OL,13,Fyear to the UK economy just stuck
OL,14,Fbehind that trust ceiling."
OL,16,FThere is little doubt that AI is
OL,17,Fchanging the world of work and the
OL,18,Fmore sophisticated it becomes, the
OL,19,Fgreater the fear over the number of
OL,20,Fjobs that will be changed or lost
OL,21,Faltogether.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"If I had to pick a timeline, I'd say
OL,7,Ffive years from now things will be
OL,8,Fvery different," he told us.
OL,10,FHe said some jobs are at more risk
OL,11,Fthan others.
OL,13,F"Clearly there are jobs that will
OL,14,Fnever be replaced - jobs where the
OL,15,Fhuman presence is a very big part of
OL,16,Fit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"There are jobs I think that are much
OL,7,Fhigher risk. I mean, if you're going
OL,8,Fto have a job as a driver, for
OL,9,Fexample, I think autonomous cars are
OL,10,Fabout to land at scale. I think if
OL,11,Fyou're a driver that job will go for
OL,12,Fsure."
OL,14,FTunstall-Pedoe says the changing face
OL,15,Fof work means some people will have to
OL,16,Fretrain but without knowing exactly
OL,17,Fwhat the future looks like, he
OL,18,Fconcedes it is difficult to know
OL,19,Fexactly what to do - or what advice to
OL,20,Fgive young people entering into the
OL,21,Fworld of work.
OL,26,@tD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"I'm not sure it's even possible to
OL,7,Fanticipate that," he said.
OL,9,F"Very often it's bits of a job that
OL,10,Fbecome automated so the AI then
OL,11,Fbecomes a tool that changes the job
OL,12,Fbut doesn't eliminate it so its
OL,13,Frelatively rare for an entire job to
OL,14,Fbe eliminated."
OL,16,FHe remains optimistic that humanity
OL,17,Fwill be able to adapt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"There will be significant changes in
OL,7,Fthe labour market and there will be
OL,8,Fsignificant changes to jobs and there
OL,9,Fwill almost certainly be fewer of
OL,10,Fcertain kinds of jobs as a result of
OL,11,Ftechnology adoption," he told us.
OL,13,F"But through history, there have been
OL,14,Ftechnology advances that have changed
OL,15,Fthe job market. This has been an
OL,16,Fabsolute constant in history, going
OL,17,Fback, you know, to automation of
OL,18,Ffarming, for example or the automation
OL,19,Fof factories.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"By and large, the world has remained
OL,12,Fin full employment. People find things
OL,13,Fto do, the economy finds jobs and
OL,14,Ffills in the market changes - but it
OL,15,Fdoesn't result in mass unemployment."
OL,17,FConcerns have been growing about an
OL,18,F"AI bubble" but Tunstall-Pedoe thinks
OL,19,Fit is here to stay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"It's not just a hype," he said. "It's
OL,7,Fnot a bubble that I think is going to
OL,8,Fburst. That doesn't mean there isn't
OL,9,Fgoing to be some kind of correction in
OL,10,Fthe stock market - who can predict
OL,11,Fthat? But the foundations of it are
OL,12,Fabsolutely real."
OL,14,FHe believes the UK is well-positioned
OL,15,Fto benefit from the AI revolution.
OL,17,F"The UK is absolutely at the forefront
OL,18,Fof Europe in AI. It has world class
OL,19,Ftalent, it has world class business
OL,20,Fenvironments," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777633372
OL,3,CUK at 'forefront' of AI in Europe,
OL,4,Csays man who taught Alexa to speak
OL,6,F"It's got the world's best
OL,7,Funiversities. So yes, we are
OL,8,Fabsolutely able to compete globally -
OL,9,Fand we should.
OL,11,F"I think there's a lot of people who
OL,12,Frecognise that the UK has got a lot of
OL,13,Fthe ingredients for that to go really
OL,14,Fwell. So there's a lot of goodwill and
OL,15,FI think we need to push hard on making
OL,16,Fit really happen."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
